"width:100%;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appJFHkxHyH4170/image/ueditor/17894600_1529975134.jpg" alt="240505_banner.jpg"/></section><section style="width:100%; margin-top:10px; display:flex; display:-webkit-flex;"><section style="width:55%;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appJFHkxHyH4170/image/ueditor/24818300_1529975134.jpg" alt="484936_banner.jpg"/></section><section style="width:45%;"><section style="padding-left: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width:100%; display:flex; display:-webkit-flex;"><section style="width: 60px; height: 60px; background-color: rgb(190, 119, 99); text-align: center; line-height: 60px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">法</section><section style="margin-left:5px;"><section style="display:flex; display:-webkit-flex;"><section style="width: 20px; height: 30px; background-color: rgb(190, 119, 99); margin-left: 5px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></section></section></section></section><p><span style="color: #262626;">金刚经<br/></span></p><p><span style="color: #262626;">与佛教的基本精神</span><br/></p></section></section></section></section></section><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: #262626;">第一，出离心。</span></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: #262626;">通过对“波罗蜜”的释义，阐述印度宗教基于六道三世轮回的生命观而特有的厌世出离的文化精神。</span></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><br/><span style="font-size: 14px; color: #262626;">第二，无我见。</span></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: #262626;">通过对“般若”的释义，阐述依据印度佛教论师龙树中观见地而建立的佛教正见：缘起与性空。</span></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><br/><span style="font-size: 14px; color: #262626;">第三，菩提心。</span></p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: #262626;">通过对《金刚经》部分经文的解说，阐述大乘佛教修行的根本：世俗谛菩提心与胜义谛菩提心的生起与修为。</span></p></section></section></section><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br/></p>

第5节_如何才能做到明心见性

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/app78b5NaK32090/a_5b99dad7e9d3c_N7OIx2H5

<p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(247, 150, 70); font-size: 14px;"></span></strong></p><section><section><section style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appJFHkxHyH4170/image/ueditor/48341200_1529975133.png" alt="默认标题_自定义cm_2017.11.28.png" style="box-shadow: rgb(102, 102, 101) 3.53553px 3.53553px 8px; margin: 0px 8px 8px 0px; border-radius: 0px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><span style="text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-size: 18px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; color: #3F3F3F;">如是我闻，一时佛在舍卫国</span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><span style="text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-size: 18px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; color: #3F3F3F;">祗树给孤独园，与大比丘众</span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><strong><span style="text-indent: 32px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; background-color: #000000; color: #FFFFFF;"> 千二百五十人俱 </span></strong></p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appJFHkxHyH4170/image/ueditor/57084300_1529975133.jpg" alt="565277_banner.jpg" style="box-shadow: rgb(102, 102, 101) 3.53553px 3.53553px 8px; margin: 0px 8px 8px 0px; border-radius: 0px;"/></p><p style="text-align: right; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: #262626;">佛告须菩提，诸菩萨摩诃萨</span></p><p style="text-align: right; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: #262626;">应如是<strong><span style="background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">降伏其心 </span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: right; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="color: #333333; text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-size: 18px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;">若卵生、若胎生、若湿生、若化生</span></p><p style="text-align: right; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="color: #333333; text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-size: 18px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;">若有色、若无色、若有想、若无想</span></p><p style="text-align: right; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="color: #333333; text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-size: 18px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;">若非有想、非无想</span></p><p style="text-align: right; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="color: #333333; text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-size: 18px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;">我皆令入无余<strong><span style="background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">涅盘而灭度之 </span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><br/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appJFHkxHyH4170/image/ueditor/64165200_1529975133.jpg" alt="离相.jpg" style="box-shadow: rgb(102, 102, 101) 3.53553px 3.53553px 8px; margin: 0px 8px 8px 0px; border-radius: 0px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><span style="text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: #262626;">如来说<strong><span style="background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">一切诸相，即是非相 </span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><span style="text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: #262626;">又说一切众生，即非众生</span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><span style="text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: #262626;">须菩提，如来是真语者</span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><span style="text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: #262626;">实语者、如语者</span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><span style="text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: #262626;">不诳语者、不异语者，</span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><span style="text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: #262626;">须菩提，如来所得法，此法无实无虚</span></p></section><section style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appJFHkxHyH4170/image/ueditor/70412500_1529975133.jpg" alt="过去心.jpg" style="box-shadow: rgb(102, 102, 101) 3.53553px 3.53553px 8px; margin: 0px 8px 8px 0px; border-radius: 0px;"/></p><p style="text-align: right; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="background-color: #F7FDFF; text-indent: 32px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: #262626;">佛告须菩提，尔所国土中</span></p><p style="text-align: right; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: #262626;">所有众生，若干种心</span></p><p style="text-align: right; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: #262626;">如来悉知</span></p><p style="text-align: right; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: #262626;">何以故，如来说诸心皆为非心</span></p><p style="text-align: right; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: #262626;">是名为心</span></p><p style="text-align: right; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: #262626;">所以者何，须菩提</span></p><p style="text-align: right; text-indent: 0em;"><strong><span style="text-indent: 32px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; background-color: #000000; color: #FFFFFF;">过去心不可得 </span></strong></p><p style="text-align: right; text-indent: 0em;"><strong><span style="text-indent: 32px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; background-color: #000000; color: #FFFFFF;">现在心不可得 </span></strong></p><p style="text-align: right; text-indent: 0em;"><strong><span style="text-indent: 32px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; background-color: #000000; color: #FFFFFF;">未来心不可得 </span></strong></p></section><section style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appJFHkxHyH4170/image/ueditor/88526500_1529975133.png" alt="平等法.png" style="box-shadow: rgb(102, 102, 101) 3.53553px 3.53553px 8px; margin: 0px 8px 8px 0px; border-radius: 0px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><span style="background-color: #F7FDFF; color: #262626; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 32px;">复次,须菩提</span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><span style="text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: #262626;">是法平等，无有高下</span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><span style="text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: #262626;">是名阿耨多罗三藐三菩提</span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><span style="text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: #262626;">以无我无人无众生无寿者</span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><span style="text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: #262626;">修一切善法</span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><span style="text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: #262626;">即得阿耨多罗三藐三菩提</span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><span style="text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: #262626;">须菩提，所言善法者</span></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><span style="text-indent: 32px; background-color: #F7FDFF; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: #262626;">如来<span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong><span style="background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">说即非善法，是名善法 </span></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><br/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appJFHkxHyH4170/image/ueditor/98849000_1529975133.png" alt="化应非真.png" style="box-shadow: rgb(102, 102, 101) 3.53553px 3.53553px 8px; margin: 0px 8px 8px 0px; border-radius: 0px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: right;"><span style="background-color: rgb(247, 253, 255); font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);">不取于相，如如不动</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: right;"><span style="background-color: rgb(247, 253, 255); font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);">何以故</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: right;"><strong><span style="font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">一切有为法，如梦幻泡影 </span></strong></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: right;"><strong><span style="font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">如露亦如电，应作如是观 </span></strong></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: right;"><span style="background-color: rgb(247, 253, 255); font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);">佛说是经已，长老须菩提</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: right;"><span style="font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: #262626;"><span style="background-color: rgb(247, 253, 255);">及诸比丘，比丘尼、</span><span style="background-color: rgb(247, 253, 255);">优婆塞、优婆夷</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: right;"><span style="background-color: rgb(247, 253, 255); font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);">一切世间天人阿修罗</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: right;"><span style="background-color: rgb(247, 253, 255); font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);">闻佛所说</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: right;"><span style="background-color: rgb(247, 253, 255); font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);">皆大欢喜，信受奉行</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><br/></p><p style="text-indent: 0em;"><br/></p><section style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; clear: both; position: relative; width: 100%; overflow: hidden;"><section style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; display: inline-block; width: 100%;"><section style="margin-left: 0.8em; float: left;"><section style="width: 2.5em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appJFHkxHyH4170/image/ueditor/6600700_1529975134.com/cache/remote/ahr0chm6ly9tbwjpei5xbg9nby5jbi9tbwjpei9jwlyyafjwdufqafftufbdeu1hzmjjzvlbrkltt2lhb2z1ylblcfr4bjfpymdpujdpynhhtezuqkhzwfvmbulnmelin1ditwczd0vmmkdqywe2vfvyzgtsqs8wp3d4x2ztdd1qcgvn"/></section><section style="margin-top: 0.5em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top;"><p class="135brush" style="padding-left: 10px; white-space: pre-wrap;    line-height: 40px;"><span style=";font-family:楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;font-size: 24px;"><strong>明师宣法</strong></span></p></section></section></section></section></section><section style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 32px; position: static;"><section style="width: 5em; height: 5em; margin: auto; padding: 8px; border-radius: 100%; box-shadow: rgb(204, 204, 204) 0px 5px 5px; background-color: rgb(254, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="border-radius: 100%; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px auto; width: 100%; padding-bottom: 100%; height: 0px; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appJFHkxHyH4170/image/ueditor/36256900_1529975133.jpg&#39;); background-position: 50% 50%; background-size: cover; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appJFHkxHyH4170/image/ueditor/12660200_1529975134.jpg" style="opacity:0;"/></section></section></section></section><p style="text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 19px;">于晓非教授</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; color: #262626; font-size: 17px;">施教于佛教名山</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; color: #262626; font-size: 17px;">地藏菩萨的道场——<strong><span style="background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">九华山 </span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 17px;">中央党校教授</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 17px;">北京大学禅学社首任名誉社长</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 17px;">亚洲最具魅力的<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>弘法居士</strong></span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><br/></p><p><span style="font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 17px;">以深厚的佛学造诣和无碍的辩才，弘传佛陀正法。对于树立正见、破斥邪说、如法修行大有裨益。</span></p><p><br/></p><section style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="padding: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width:100%;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appJFHkxHyH4170/image/ueditor/17894600_1529975134.jpg" alt="240505_banner.jpg"/></section><section style="width:100%; margin-top:10px; display:flex; display:-webkit-flex;"><section style="width:55%;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appJFHkxHyH4170/image/ueditor/24818300_1529975134.jpg" alt="484936_banner.jpg"/></section><section style="width:45%;"><section style="padding-left: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width:100%; display:flex; display:-webkit-flex;"><section style="width: 60px; height: 60px; background-color: rgb(190, 119, 99); text-align: center; line-height: 60px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">法</section><section style="margin-left:5px;"><section style="display:flex; display:-webkit-flex;"><section style="width: 20px; height: 30px; background-color: rgb(190, 119, 99); margin-left: 5px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></section></section></section></section><p><span style="color: #262626;">金刚经<br/></span></p><p><span style="color: #262626;">与佛教的基本精神</span><br/></p></section></section></section></section></section><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: #262626;">第一，出离心。</span></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: #262626;">通过对“波罗蜜”的释义，阐述印度宗教基于六道三世轮回的生命观而特有的厌世出离的文化精神。</span></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><br/><span style="font-size: 14px; color: #262626;">第二，无我见。</span></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: #262626;">通过对“般若”的释义，阐述依据印度佛教论师龙树中观见地而建立的佛教正见：缘起与性空。</span></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><br/><span style="font-size: 14px; color: #262626;">第三，菩提心。</span></p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: #262626;">通过对《金刚经》部分经文的解说，阐述大乘佛教修行的根本：世俗谛菩提心与胜义谛菩提心的生起与修为。</span></p></section></section></section><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br/></p>

第6节_常见与断见

